dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represents building footprints for Dane County, Wisconsin in 2005. The dataset was originally published by the Dane County Land Information Office on May 31, 2011.[This dataset contains building polygon data for Dane County. The dataset consists of structures the size of a single car garage or larger for Dane County, WI excluding structures within the City of Madison. In the City of Madison, building polygons are included for structures the size of a duplex or larger, except for around the Isthmus area.]
